  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>Unwrap Canada's pleasant mix of Old world charm and vibrant cities on this escorted tour through Eastern Canada. Expect world-class attractions, impressive architecture and fine fashion and cuisine. You'll skirt and admire the Laurentian Mountains, </span><span>majestic St. Lawrence River and tulip-lined waterways as you hop from city to city stopping off at fantastic sites along the way. </span><span>This journey delivers natural beauty, charm and urban thrills.</span></p>
<div>
<p><strong>Maximum Group Size: 50</strong></p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-canada/eastern-journey-escorted-tour#Tour highlights">Tour highlights</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-canada/eastern-journey-escorted-tour#Itinerary">Itinerary</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-canada/eastern-journey-escorted-tour#Your holiday includes">Your holiday includes</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-canada/eastern-journey-escorted-tour#Hotels">Hotels </a>| <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-canada/eastern-journey-escorted-tour#Departure dates">Departure dates</a></h2>
